org.apache.hadoop.hbase.wal

Interface WALKey

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<WALKey>, SequenceId
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WALKeyImpl

    @InterfaceAudience.LimitedPrivate(value={"Replication","Coprocesssor"})
public interface WALKey
extends SequenceId, Comparable<WALKey>
    Key for WAL Entry. Read-only. No Setters. For limited audience such as Coprocessors.
